I've worked with Shen Yifan's PR team

00:03:50.840 --> 00:03:52.480
to develop five contingency plans.

00:03:52.480 --> 00:03:54.120
No matter what they release today,

00:03:54.120 --> 00:03:55.240
we have ways to counter it.

00:03:55.240 --> 00:03:56.000
Got it.

00:03:56.920 --> 00:03:58.160
Even if the sky falls,

00:03:58.440 --> 00:04:00.700
I, Yu Youyi, will be there to support her.

