Let's have a moment of honesty before you go.

00:06:09.920 --> 00:06:14.050
A talented graduate from the Film Academy's cinematography department.

00:06:14.080 --> 00:06:16.810
Documentaries winning numerous awards abroad.

00:06:16.960 --> 00:06:20.290
The most promising new-generation documentary director.

00:06:22.920 --> 00:06:23.880
That was before.

00:06:25.600 --> 00:06:27.920
No wonder the comic leak mentioned

00:06:27.920 --> 00:06:30.180
a mysterious man with a double identity.

00:06:30.920 --> 00:06:32.560
So you went from documentary director

00:06:32.560 --> 00:06:34.620
to suddenly becoming a talent agent.

00:06:34.760 --> 00:06:35.360
Tell me,

00:06:36.000 --> 00:06:37.000
being by my side,

00:06:37.000 --> 00:06:38.800
are you on some secret mission?

00:06:40.880 --> 00:06:42.000
I just...

00:06:44.640 --> 00:06:45.960
I ran out of creativity

00:06:46.600 --> 00:06:48.720
and changed careers to make a living.

00:06:54.440 --> 00:06:55.480
What's with that look?

00:06:55.480 --> 00:06:58.480
This is my 'I don't believe a word you're saying' face.

00:06:59.240 --> 00:07:00.120
Dad,

00:07:00.360 --> 00:07:02.000
