Well, you wanted to come,

00:12:28.520 --> 00:12:30.400
so I had to agree.

00:12:32.400 --> 00:12:34.480
How about Uncle Wu Yu takes you to see the fish?

00:12:34.480 --> 00:12:35.000
Okay.

00:12:37.960 --> 00:12:38.520
Let's go.

00:12:39.000 --> 00:12:40.160
Come with me to see the fish.

00:12:40.160 --> 00:12:40.600
Off we go.

00:12:40.600 --> 00:12:41.520
Let's go.

